{
  "stem": "7938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened-- the first two days I was so knocked down, and so depressed, that I didn't even go out of the house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was staying in bed for two days, dressed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't undress.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And finally, after two days, I went out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And pretty soon, we knew already that really, there was a tragedy, what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a real-- a real [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] what they called, and that the people some-- there was a boxer in Warsaw, a Jewish boxer, Rotholz, who went also with the same transport.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he ran away in the-- on the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He jumped out of the car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then later on, he mixed with the Polish population, and he got the information what happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he knew already, he told us that the transport went to-- to Belzec, and that nobody knew what was inside, because the crew of the train was changed from the regular crew.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They put a German crew inside, soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they knew-- they told him that after one day, the train came back empty.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And after a few days, a few weeks, nobody, nothing, was brought in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody was taken out from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nobody knew what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we understood that probably they were all dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- and he came into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Apparently, he found himself in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- that's why he was there At that time, after this, I started looking for work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got some work outside of the ghetto in a-- in a-- it's supposed to be a very good job because it was for the army.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got the permission to go out every day.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
